{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"1.05","c":"اقْتَرَبَتِ","d":"qٱtْrَbَtَِ","e":"iq'tarabati"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.75","c":"السَّاعَةُ","d":"lٱsāَّعʿẗَُ","e":"l-sāʿatu"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.64","c":"وَانْشَقَّ","d":"wnٱَshqََّ","e":"wa-inshaqqa"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.92","c":"الْقَمَرُ","d":"lٱqْmَrَُ","e":"l-qamaru"}],"a":{"g":"The Hour has come near, and the moon has split [in two]."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"وَإِنْ","d":"wʾَinِ","e":"wa-in"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.44","c":"يَرَوْا","d":"yrَwَāْ۟","e":"yaraw"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.4","c":"ءَايَةً","d":"ءāَyẗًَ","e":"āyatan"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.53","c":"يُعْرِضُوا","d":"yعُʿrْḍِwُā۟","e":"yuʿ'riḍū"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.37","c":"وَيَقُولُوا","d":"wyَqَwُlwُā۟","e":"wayaqūlū"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.36","c":"سِحْرٌ","d":"sḥِrٌْ","e":"siḥ'run"},{"b":"7.9","h":"10.25","c":"مُسْتَمِرٌّ","d":"msُّtْmَrٌِّ","e":"mus'tamirrun"}],"a":{"g":"And if they see a miracle, they turn away and say, \"Passing magic.\""}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"وَكَذَّبُوا","d":"wkَdَhbَّwُā۟","e":"wakadhabū"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.54","c":"وَاتَّبَعُوا","d":"wtٱَbَّعَʿwُāٓ۟","e":"wa-ittabaʿū"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.56","c":"أَهْوَاءَهُمْ","d":"ʾahَwْāَءٓhَmُْ","e":"ahwāahum"},{"b":"7.3","h":"11.4","c":"وَكُلُّ","d":"wkَlُُّ","e":"wakullu"},{"b":"8.1","h":"12.62","c":"أَمْرٍ","d":"ʾamَrٍْ","e":"amrin"},{"b":"10.","h":"14.69","c":"مُسْتَقِرٌّ","d":"msُّtْqَrٌِّ","e":"mus'taqirrun"}],"a":{"g":"And they denied and followed their inclinations. But for every matter is a [time of] settlement."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.08","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"wlَqَdَْ","e":"walaqad"},{"b":"0.81","h":"1.36","c":"جَاءَهُمْ","d":"gjāَءٓhَmُ","e":"jāahum"},{"b":"3.9","h":"4.49","c":"مِنَ","d":"mnَِّ","e":"mina"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.05","c":"الْأَنْبَاءِ","d":"lٱʾْanَbۢāَءِٓ","e":"l-anbāi"},{"b":"8.3","h":"8.61","c":"مَا","d":"māَ","e":"mā"},{"b":"8.7","h":"9.29","c":"فِيهِ","d":"fyِhِ","e":"fīhi"},{"b":"9.5","h":"10.6","c":"مُزْدَجَرٌ","d":"mzُdْgَjrٌَ","e":"muz'dajarun"}],"a":{"g":"And there has already come to them of information that in which there is deterrence -"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","h":"0.45","c":"حِكْمَةٌ","d":"ḥkِmْẗٌَۢ","e":"ḥik'matun"},{"b":"2.1","h":"2.41","c":"بَالِغَةٌ","d":"blَٰغِẗٌَ","e":"bālighatun"},{"b":"4.4","h":"5.1","c":"فَمَا","d":"fmَāَ","e":"famā"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.31","c":"تُغْنِ","d":"tغُnِْ","e":"tugh'ni"},{"b":"5.9","h":"7.45","c":"النُّذُرُ","d":"lٱndُّhrُُ","e":"l-nudhuru"}],"a":{"g":"Extensive wisdom - but warning does not avail [them]."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.3","c":"فَتَوَلَّ","d":"ftَwَlََّ","e":"fatawalla"},{"b":"0.96","h":"2.78","c":"عَنْهُمْ","d":"عʿnَhْmُْ","e":"ʿanhum"},{"b":"2.5","h":"6.8","c":"يَوْمَ","d":"ywَmَْ","e":"yawma"},{"b":"3.1","h":"7.72","c":"يَدْعُ","d":"ydَعْʿُ","e":"yadʿu"},{"b":"3.8","h":"8.8","c":"الدَّاعِ","d":"lٱdāَّعʿِ","e":"l-dāʿi"},{"b":"4.7","h":"10.66","c":"إِلَى","d":"ʾilِàَٰ","e":"ilā"},{"b":"5.3","h":"11.42","c":"شَيْءٍ","d":"shàَءٍْ","e":"shayin"},{"b":"6.9","h":"12.89","c":"نُكُرٍ","d":"nkُّrٍُ","e":"nukurin"}],"a":{"g":"So leave them, [O Muhammad]. The Day the Caller calls to something forbidding,"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"خُشَّعًا","d":"khsُhعَّʿāً","e":"khushaʿan"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.48","c":"أَبْصَارُهُمْ","d":"ʾabَṣْrَٰhُmُْ","e":"abṣāruhum"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.86","c":"يَخْرُجُونَ","d":"ykَhrْgُjwُnَ","e":"yakhrujūna"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.87","c":"مِنَ","d":"mnَِ","e":"mina"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.49","c":"الْأَجْدَاثِ","d":"lٱʾْagَjdْāَthِ","e":"l-ajdāthi"},{"b":"5.6","h":"8.47","c":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","d":"kʾَanَhَّmُْ","e":"ka-annahum"},{"b":"7.8","h":"10.72","c":"جَرَادٌ","d":"gjrَāَdٌ","e":"jarādun"},{"b":"11.0","h":"13.02","c":"مُنْتَشِرٌ","d":"mnُّtsَhrٌِ","e":"muntashirun"}],"a":{"g":"Their eyes humbled, they will emerge from the graves as if they were locusts spreading,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.64","c":"مُهْطِعِينَ","d":"mhُّṭْعِʿyِnَ","e":"muh'ṭiʿīna"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.3","c":"إِلَى","d":"ʾilِàَ","e":"ilā"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.21","c":"الدَّاعِ","d":"lٱdāَّعʿِ","e":"l-dāʿi"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.7","c":"يَقُولُ","d":"yqَwُlُ","e":"yaqūlu"},{"b":"5.4","h":"8","c":"الْكَافِرُونَ","d":"lٱkْfَٰrِwُnَ","e":"l-kāfirūna"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.35","c":"هَذَا","d":"hdَٰhāَ","e":"hādhā"},{"b":"7.8","h":"12.05","c":"يَوْمٌ","d":"ywَmٌْ","e":"yawmun"},{"b":"8.7","h":"13.43","c":"عَسِرٌ","d":"عʿsَrٌِ","e":"ʿasirun"}],"a":{"g":"Racing ahead toward the Caller. The disbelievers will say, \"This is a difficult Day.\""}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"kdَhbَّtَْ","e":"kadhabat"},{"b":"0.98","h":"1.83","c":"قَبْلَهُمْ","d":"qbَlْhَmُْ","e":"qablahum"},{"b":"2.0","h":"3.38","c":"قَوْمُ","d":"qwَmُْ","e":"qawmu"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.43","c":"نُوحٍ","d":"nwُḥٍ","e":"nūḥin"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.15","c":"فَكَذَّبُوا","d":"fkَdَhbَّwُā۟","e":"fakadhabū"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.25","c":"عَبْدَنَا","d":"عʿbَdْnَāَ","e":"ʿabdanā"},{"b":"6.6","h":"9.93","c":"وَقَالُوا","d":"wqَāَlwُā۟","e":"waqālū"},{"b":"7.8","h":"11.76","c":"مَجْنُونٌ","d":"mgَjnْwُnٌ","e":"majnūnun"},{"b":"9.0","h":"14.18","c":"وَازْدُجِرَ","d":"wzٱَdْgُjrَِ","e":"wa-uz'dujira"}],"a":{"g":"The people of Noah denied before them, and they denied Our servant and said, \"A madman,\" and he was repelled."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فَدَعَا","d":"fdَعَʿāَ","e":"fadaʿā"},{"b":"0.79","h":"2.03","c":"رَبَّهُ","d":"rbَhَّۥُٓ","e":"rabbahu"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.94","c":"أَنِّي","d":"ʾanَàِّ","e":"annī"},{"b":"4.8","h":"6.81","c":"مَغْلُوبٌ","d":"mغَlْwُbٌ","e":"maghlūbun"},{"b":"6.9","h":"9.59","c":"فَانْتَصِرْ","d":"fnٱَtṣَrِْ","e":"fa-intaṣir"}],"a":{"g":"So he invoked his Lord, \"Indeed, I am overpowered, so help.\""}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"فَفَتَحْنَا","d":"ffَtَḥَnْāَٓ","e":"fafataḥnā"},{"b":"2.9","h":"1.69","c":"أَبْوَابَ","d":"ʾabَwْbََٰ","e":"abwāba"},{"b":"3.9","h":"5.2","c":"السَّمَاءِ","d":"lٱsmَّāَءِٓ","e":"l-samāi"},{"b":"6.5","h":"7.79","c":"بِمَاءٍ","d":"bmِāَءٍٓ","e":"bimāin"},{"b":"10.8","h":"10.77","c":"مُنْهَمِرٍ","d":"mnُّhْmَrٍِ","e":"mun'hamirin"}],"a":{"g":"Then We opened the gates of the heaven with rain pouring down"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"وَفَجَّرْنَا","d":"wfَgَjrَّnْāَ","e":"wafajjarnā"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.35","c":"الْأَرْضَ","d":"lٱʾْarَḍَْ","e":"l-arḍa"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.63","c":"عُيُونًا","d":"عʿyُwُnāً","e":"ʿuyūnan"},{"b":"4.0","h":"5.94","c":"فَالْتَقَى","d":"flٱَtْqَàَ","e":"fal-taqā"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.45","c":"الْمَاءُ","d":"lٱmْāَءُٓ","e":"l-māu"},{"b":"7.1","h":"9.75","c":"عَلَى","d":"عʿlَàَٰٓ","e":"ʿalā"},{"b":"9.3","h":"11.94","c":"أَمْرٍ","d":"ʾamَrٍْ","e":"amrin"},{"b":"11.2","h":"13.66","c":"قَدْ","d":"qdَْ","e":"qad"},{"b":"11.6","h":"14.33","c":"قُدِرَ","d":"qdُrَِ","e":"qudira"}],"a":{"g":"And caused the earth to burst with springs, and the waters met for a matter already predestined."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَحَمَلْنَاهُ","d":"wḥَmَlَnْhَُٰ","e":"waḥamalnāhu"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.6","c":"عَلَى","d":"عʿlَàَٰ","e":"ʿalā"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.7","c":"ذَاتِ","d":"dhāَtِ","e":"dhāti"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.89","c":"أَلْوَاحٍ","d":"ʾalَwْḥٍَٰ","e":"alwāḥin"},{"b":"4.1","h":"7.36","c":"وَدُسُرٍ","d":"wdَsُrٍُ","e":"wadusurin"}],"a":{"g":"And We carried him on a [construction of] planks and nails,"}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"تَجْرِي","d":"tgَjrْàِ","e":"tajrī"},{"b":"0.84","h":"1.98","c":"بِأَعْيُنِنَا","d":"bʾِaعَʿyْnُnِāَ","e":"bi-aʿyuninā"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.41","c":"جَزَاءً","d":"gjzَāَءًٓ","e":"jazāan"},{"b":"5.2","h":"7.02","c":"لِمَنْ","d":"lmِّnَ","e":"liman"},{"b":"6.7","h":"8.79","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"7.4","h":"10","c":"كُفِرَ","d":"kfُrَِ","e":"kufira"}],"a":{"g":"Sailing under Our observation as reward for he who had been denied."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.4","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"wlَqَdَ","e":"walaqad"},{"b":"0.62","h":"2.2","c":"تَرَكْنَاهَا","d":"trَّkَnْhَٰāَٓ","e":"taraknāhā"},{"b":"3.5","h":"6.09","c":"ءَايَةً","d":"ءāَyẗًَ","e":"āyatan"},{"b":"5.9","h":"9.6","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"fhَlَْ","e":"fahal"},{"b":"6.6","h":"10.55","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِ","e":"min"},{"b":"8.0","h":"11.98","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"mdُّkَّrٍِ","e":"muddakirin"}],"a":{"g":"And We left it as a sign, so is there any who will remember?"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"fkَyَfَْ","e":"fakayfa"},{"b":"0.82","h":"1.6","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.62","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"عʿdَhāَbàِ","e":"ʿadhābī"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.42","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"wnَdُhrُِ","e":"wanudhuri"}],"a":{"g":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.7","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"wlَqَdَْ","e":"walaqad"},{"b":"0.79","h":"1.87","c":"يَسَّرْنَا","d":"ysَrَّnْāَ","e":"yassarnā"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.59","c":"الْقُرْءَانَ","d":"lٱqْrُءْāَnَ","e":"l-qur'āna"},{"b":"3.4","h":"5.74","c":"لِلذِّكْرِ","d":"llِdhkِّrِْ","e":"lildhik'ri"},{"b":"4.4","h":"7.39","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"fhَlَْ","e":"fahal"},{"b":"5.1","h":"8.55","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِ","e":"min"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.03","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"mdُّkَّrٍِ","e":"muddakirin"}],"a":{"g":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ولكونه حاضرا في القلب ومنسيا بالشغل عنه سمي الله تعالى جميع معارف الإيمان تذكرا فقال تعالى: ﴿ ولقد يسرنا القران للذكر فهل من مدكر ﴾ {} فهذا هو علاج الصبر عن الوساوس والشواغل وهو آخر درجات الصبر وإنما الصبر عن العلائق كلها مقدم على الصبر عن الخواطر.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, because it is present within the heart [qalb] yet forgotten due to preoccupation away from it, Allah the Exalted has named all the knowledges [ma'arif] of faith a remembrance [tadhkira]. Thus He, the Exalted, said: \"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance [dhikr]. So is there any who will remember [mudhakir]?\" (54:17). This, then, is the remedy for patience [sabr] from whisperings and preoccupations, and it is the final degree of patience. For indeed, patience from all attachments is a prerequisite for patience from passing thoughts.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"kdَhbَّtَْ","e":"kadhabat"},{"b":"1","h":"2.19","c":"عَادٌ","d":"عʿāَdٌ","e":"ʿādun"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.01","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"fkَyَfَْ","e":"fakayfa"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.44","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.47","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"عʿdَhāَbàِ","e":"ʿadhābī"},{"b":"5.4","h":"8.65","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"wnَdُhrُِ","e":"wanudhuri"}],"a":{"g":"'Aad denied; and how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"إِنَّا","d":"ʾinِāَّٓ","e":"innā"},{"b":"1.1","h":"3.19","c":"أَرْسَلْنَا","d":"ʾarَsْlَnْāَ","e":"arsalnā"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.28","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"عʿlَyَhْmِْ","e":"ʿalayhim"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.09","c":"رِيحًا","d":"ryِḥāً","e":"rīḥan"},{"b":"6.8","h":"8.8","c":"صَرْصَرًا","d":"ṣrَṣْrَāً","e":"ṣarṣaran"},{"b":"8.6","h":"10.94","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"9.2","h":"11.73","c":"يَوْمِ","d":"ywَmِْ","e":"yawmi"},{"b":"9.8","h":"12.76","c":"نَحْسٍ","d":"nḥَsٍْ","e":"naḥsin"},{"b":"11.6","h":"14.69","c":"مُسْتَمِرٍّ","d":"msُّtْmَrٍِّ","e":"mus'tamirrin"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind on a day of continuous misfortune,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ومن آياته الهواء اللطيف المحبوس بين مقعر السماء ومحدب الأرض يدرك بحس اللمس عند هبوب الرياح جسمه ولا يرى بالمين شخصه وجملته مثل البحر الواحد والطيور محلقة فى جو السماء ومستبقة سباحة فيه بأجنحتها كما تسبح حيوانات البحر فى الماء وتضطرب جوانبه وأمواجه عند هبوب الرياح كما تضطرب أمواج البحر فإذا حرك الله الهواء وجعله ريحا هابة فإن شاء جعله نشرابين يدى رحمته كما قال سبحانه وأرسلنا الرياح لواقح فيصل بحركته روح الهواء إلى الحيوانات والنباتات فتستعد للنماء وإن شاء جعله عذابا على العصاة من خليقته كما قال تعالى إنا أرسلنا عليهم ريحا صرصرا فى يوم نحس مستمر تنزع الناس كأنهم أعجاز نخل منقعر\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                And from His signs [ayat] is the subtle air [al-hawa' al-latif], confined between the concave of the sky and the convex of the earth. Its substance is perceived by the sense of touch when the winds blow, yet its form is not seen by the eye. Its totality is like a single sea, and the birds soar in the atmosphere of the sky, racing in swimming through it with their wings, just as the creatures of the sea swim in water. And its sides and its waves are agitated when the winds blow, just as the waves of the sea are agitated. So when God sets the air in motion and makes it a blowing wind, then if He wills, He makes it a herald [nashiran] preceding His mercy, as He, the Glorified, said: 'And We send the fertilizing winds.' Thus, through its motion, the spirit [ruh] of the air reaches the animals and the plants, and they become prepared for growth. And if He wills, He makes it a punishment ['adhab] upon the disobedient from His creation, as God, the Exalted, said: 'Indeed, We sent upon them a screaming wind, on a day of unceasing calamity, plucking the people as if they were trunks of uprooted palm trees.'\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"تَنْزِعُ","d":"tnَzعِʿُ","e":"tanziʿu"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.23","c":"النَّاسَ","d":"lٱnāَّsَ","e":"l-nāsa"},{"b":"3","h":"3.91","c":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","d":"kʾَanَhَّmُْ","e":"ka-annahum"},{"b":"5.0","h":"6.23","c":"أَعْجَازُ","d":"ʾaعَʿgْjāَzُ","e":"aʿjāzu"},{"b":"6.1","h":"8.02","c":"نَخْلٍ","d":"nkَhlٍْ","e":"nakhlin"},{"b":"7.6","h":"10.03","c":"مُنْقَعِرٍ","d":"mnُّqعَʿrٍِ","e":"munqaʿirin"}],"a":{"g":"Extracting the people as if they were trunks of palm trees uprooted."}},"21":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"فَكَيْفَ","d":"fkَyَfَْ","e":"fakayfa"},{"b":"0.79","h":"1.95","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāَnَ","e":"kāna"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.94","c":"عَذَابِي","d":"عʿdَhāَbàِ","e":"ʿadhābī"},{"b":"2.6","h":"5.02","c":"وَنُذُرِ","d":"wnَdُhrُِ","e":"wanudhuri"}],"a":{"g":"And how [severe] were My punishment and warning."}},"22":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وَلَقَدْ","d":"wlَqَdَْ","e":"walaqad"},{"b":"0.78","h":"1.48","c":"يَسَّرْنَا","d":"ysَrَّnْāَ","e":"yassarnā"},{"b":"2","h":"3.2","c":"الْقُرْءَانَ","d":"lٱqْrُءْāَnَ","e":"l-qur'āna"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.44","c":"لِلذِّكْرِ","d":"llِdhkِّrِْ","e":"lildhik'ri"},{"b":"4.3","h":"7.07","c":"فَهَلْ","d":"fhَlَْ","e":"fahal"},{"b":"5.0","h":"8.21","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِ","e":"min"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.04","c":"مُدَّكِرٍ","d":"mdُّkَّrٍِ","e":"muddakirin"}],"a":{"g":"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember?"}},"23":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"كَذَّبَتْ","d":"kdَhbَّtَْ","e":"kadhabat"},{"b":"0.98","h":"2.37","c":"ثَمُودُ","d":"thmَwُdُ","e":"thamūdu"},{"b":"1.9","h":"4.83","c":"بِالنُّذُرِ","d":"blٱِndُّhrُِ","e":"bil-nudhuri"}],"a":{"g":"Thamud denied the warning"}},"24":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"فَقَالُوا","d":"fqَāَlwُāٓ۟","e":"faqālū"},{"b":"2.1","h":"2.55","c":"أَبَشَرًا","d":"ʾabَsَhrَāً","e":"abasharan"},{"b":"3.0","h":"3.84","c":"مِنَّا","d":"mnِّāَّ","e":"minnā"},{"b":"5.2","h":"6.37","c":"وَاحِدًا","d":"wḥَٰdِāً","e":"wāḥidan"},{"b":"6.2","h":"7.72","c":"نَتَّبِعُهُ","d":"ntَّbَّعِʿhُۥُٓ","e":"nattabiʿuhu"},{"b":"10.0","h":"11.65","c":"إِنَّا","d":"ʾinِāَّٓ","e":"innā"},{"b":"11.2","h":"14.24","c":"إِذًا","d":"ʾidِhāً","e":"idhan"},{"b":"13.2","h":"14.92","c":"لَفِي","d":"lfَّàِ","e":"lafī"},{"b":"14.1","h":"16.3","c":"ضَلَالٍ","d":"ḍlَlٍَٰ","e":"ḍalālin"},{"b":"15.3","h":"18.67","c":"وَسُعُرٍ","d":"wsَعُʿrٍُ","e":"wasuʿurin"}],"a":{"g":"And said, \"Is it one human being among us that we should follow? Indeed, we would then be in error and madness.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وقوله تعالى: ﴿ أبشرا منا واحدا نتبعه ﴾ فهذه المعميات هى التى منعت الاهتداء\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, \"A human [bashar] from among us, one, shall we follow him?\" So these blindings [al-'amawiyyat] are what prevented the guidance [al-hidaya].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"25":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"أَءُلْقِيَ","d":"ʾaءَlُqْàَِ","e":"a-ul'qiya"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.84","c":"الذِّكْرُ","d":"lٱdhkِّrُْ","e":"l-dhik'ru"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.72","c":"عَلَيْهِ","d":"عʿlَyَhِْ","e":"ʿalayhi"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.23","c":"مِنْ","d":"mnِۢ","e":"min"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.18","c":"بَيْنِنَا","d":"byَnْnِāَ","e":"bayninā"},{"b":"4.9","h":"6.94","c":"بَلْ","d":"blَْ","e":"bal"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.64","c":"هُوَ","d":"hwَُ","e":"huwa"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.27","c":"كَذَّابٌ","d":"kdَhāَّbٌ","e":"kadhābun"},{"b":"7.1","h":"10.58","c":"أَشِرٌ","d":"ʾasَhrٌِ","e":"ashirun"}],"a":{"g":"Has the message been sent down upon him from among us? Rather, he is an insolent liar.\""}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"سَيَعْلَمُونَ","d":"syَعَʿlْmَwُnَ","e":"sayaʿlamūna"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.7","c":"غَدًا","d":"غdَāً","e":"ghadan"},{"b":"1.9","h":"3.34","c":"مَنِ","d":"mnَِّ","e":"mani"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.5","c":"الْكَذَّابُ","d":"lٱkْdَhāَّbُ","e":"l-kadhābu"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.73","c":"الْأَشِرُ","d":"lٱʾْasَhrُِ","e":"l-ashiru"}],"a":{"g":"They will know tomorrow who is the insolent liar."}},"27":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"إِنَّا","d":"ʾinِāَّ","e":"innā"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.07","c":"مُرْسِلُوا","d":"mrُsْlِwُā۟","e":"mur'silū"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.67","c":"النَّاقَةِ","d":"lٱnāَّqẗَِ","e":"l-nāqati"},{"b":"4.1","h":"5.39","c":"فِتْنَةً","d":"ftِnْẗًَ","e":"fit'natan"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.87","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"lhَّmُْ","e":"lahum"},{"b":"5.9","h":"8.14","c":"فَارْتَقِبْهُمْ","d":"frٱَtْqَbِhْmُْ","e":"fa-ir'taqib'hum"},{"b":"7.5","h":"10.62","c":"وَاصْطَبِرْ","d":"wṣٱَṭْbَrِْ","e":"wa-iṣ'ṭabir"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We are sending the she-camel as trial for them, so watch them and be patient."}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"وَنَبِّئْهُمْ","d":"wnَbَʾِّyhْmُْ","e":"wanabbi'hum"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.69","c":"أَنَّ","d":"ʾanََّ","e":"anna"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.12","c":"الْمَاءَ","d":"lٱmْāَءَٓ","e":"l-māa"},{"b":"5.7","h":"6.28","c":"قِسْمَةٌ","d":"qsِmْẗٌَۢ","e":"qis'matun"},{"b":"7.6","h":"8.62","c":"بَيْنَهُمْ","d":"byَnْhَmُْ","e":"baynahum"},{"b":"8.7","h":"12.4","c":"كُلُّ","d":"klُُّ","e":"kullu"},{"b":"9.3","h":"13.27","c":"شِرْبٍ","d":"shrِbٍْ","e":"shir'bin"},{"b":"11.2","h":"15.5","c":"مُحْتَضَرٌ","d":"mḥُّtْḍَrٌَ","e":"muḥ'taḍarun"}],"a":{"g":"And inform them that the water is shared between them, each [day of] drink attended [by turn]."}},"29":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَنَادَوْا","d":"fnَāَdwَāْ۟","e":"fanādaw"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.46","c":"صَاحِبَهُمْ","d":"ṣāَḥbِhَmُْ","e":"ṣāḥibahum"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.53","c":"فَتَعَاطَى","d":"ftَعَ