"l-zuburi"}],"a":{"g":"And everything they did is in written records."}},"53":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.26","c":"وَكُلُّ","d":"wkَlُُّ","e":"wakullu"},{"b":"0.83","h":"1.65","c":"صَغِيرٍ","d":"ṣغَyِrٍ","e":"ṣaghīrin"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.99","c":"وَكَبِيرٍ","d":"wkَbَyِrٍ","e":"wakabīrin"},{"b":"4.5","h":"7.08","c":"مُسْتَطَرٌ","d":"msُّtْṭَrٌَ","e":"mus'taṭarun"}],"a":{"g":"And every small and great [thing] is inscribed."}},"54":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"إِنَّ","d":"ʾinَِّ","e":"inna"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.51","c":"الْمُتَّقِينَ","d":"lٱmْtُqَّyِnَ","e":"l-mutaqīna"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.15","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.07","c":"جَنَّاتٍ","d":"gjnَtٍَّٰ","e":"jannātin"},{"b":"5.3","h":"8.42","c":"وَنَهَرٍ","d":"wnَhَrٍَ","e":"wanaharin"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, the righteous will be among gardens and rivers,"}},"55":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.03","c":"فِي","d":"fàِ","e":"fī"},{"b":"0.52","h":"0.66","c":"مَقْعَدِ","d":"mqَعْʿdَِ","e":"maqʿadi"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.13","c":"صِدْقٍ","d":"ṣdِqٍْ","e":"ṣid'qin"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.71","c":"عِنْدَ","d":"عʿnِdَ","e":"ʿinda"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.59","c":"مَلِيكٍ","d":"mlَyِkٍ","e":"malīkin"},{"b":"6.0","h":"8.22","c":"مُقْتَدِرٍ","d":"mqُّtْdَrٍِۭ","e":"muq'tadirin"}],"a":{"g":"In a seat of honor near a Sovereign, Perfect in Ability.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ومن كان مقصده رب الدار ومالك الملك ولم يغلب عليه إلا حبه بالإخلاص والصدق، أنزل \" في مقعد صدق عند مليك مقتدر \" فالأبرار يرتعون في البساتين ويتنعمون في الجنان مع الحور العين والولدان، والمقربون ملازمون للحضرة عاكفون بطرفهم عليها يستحقرون نعيم الجنان بالإضافة إلى ذرة منها فقوم بقضاء شهوة البطن والفرج مشغولون، وللمجالسة أقوام آخرون، ولذلك قال رسول الله ﭬ: \" أكثر أهل الجنة البله وعليون لذوي الألباب\" ولما قصرت الأفهام عن درك معنى عليين عظم أمره فقال: \" وما أدراك ما عليون \" كما قال تعالى: \" القارعة ما القارعة وما أدراك ما القارعة \".\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, he whose aim is the Lord of the Abode [rabb al-dar] and the Possessor of Sovereignty [malik al-mulk], and who is overcome by nothing but His love through sincerity [ikhlas] and truthfulness [sidq], He will cause to dwell \"in a seat of truth [fi maq'ad sidq], near a Sovereign Omnipotent [mulk muqtadir].\" Thus, the righteous [al-abrar] will roam in gardens and delight in paradises with wide-eyed maidens and immortal youths. But those brought near [al-muqarrabun] are constant in the Presence [al-hadra], their gaze fixed upon It, and they deem the bliss of the gardens insignificant compared to an atom of It. For some people are preoccupied with satisfying the appetite of the belly and the private parts, while others are for intimate companionship [mujalasa]. And for this reason, the Messenger of God, peace and blessings be upon him, said: \"The majority of the inhabitants of Paradise are the simple-minded, and 'Illiyyun is for those of intellect.\" And when understandings fell short of grasping the meaning of 'Illiyyun, He magnified its matter, saying: \"And what will make you know what 'Illiyyun is?\" just as the Almighty has said: \"The Striking Calamity! What is the Striking Calamity? And what will make you know what the Striking Calamity is?\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}}}